root: ^Aww, see anak?  I told you not to eat too much spaghetti graw pow. Now you have an upset stomach.
^*laugh* I'm glad you liked it, but your mother is right. Gotta take your time when it comes to good food.
^The spaghetti won't be going anywhere, and we can always make it again, so don't worry about it running away or anything.
^Next time, eat slower but enjoy every single bite.
^Good. Now rest up, and your tummy will feel all better when you wake up. Good night, Jay.
